==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Housemaid
<hw>House"maid`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A female servant
employed to do housework, esp. to take care of the rooms.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Housemaid's knee</b></col> <fld>(Med.)</fld>, <cd>a
swelling over the knee, due to an enlargement of the bursa in the front
of the kneepan; -- so called because frequently occurring in servant
girls who work upon their knees.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>houseman</ent>⟦br⟧
